Nidalee_0: Raised in the deepest jungle, Nidalee is a master tracker who can shapeshift into a ferocious cougar at will. Neither wholly woman nor beast, she viciously defends her territory from any and all trespassers, with carefully placed traps and deft spear throws. She cripples her quarry before pouncing on them in feline form - the lucky few who survive tell tales of a wild woman with razor-sharp instincts, and even sharper claws...
Nidalee_1: A fierce warrior who makes her home in the winter forest, Nidalee isn't content with simple Snowdown parties. She plays the role of Santa for cheery woodland creatures, driving off intruders and protecting her furry friends from harm.
Nidalee_4: At the height of her power, Nidalee was worshipped as a god-queen of the Great Desert. After her city's fall, she gathered her remaining armies and marched west, to conquer and rule anew.
Nidalee_5: She is a cat. That is a hat. Legally, we're not allowed to put those two thoughts together.
Nidalee_6: It's one thing to be hunted by a human; it's another to be chased down by an animal. Nidalee's alien biology allows her both - a rare gift among the Headhunters.
Nidalee_7: A wild, untamed fighter steeped in myth, it is difficult to know what is true of Nidalee and what is legend. Some say she fights with the ferocity of a white tiger, while others of the Warring Kingdoms believe she can become the creature itself.
Nidalee_9: Nidalee shows the most promise of the new class of Super Galaxy cadets, a knack for throwing projectiles through zero-gravity being her signature talent. The team will need her cunning tactics, as well as her keen hunting instincts, if it is to defeat the Spider Queen.
Nidalee_11: Nidalee rules over the restorative calm of the natural world, guarding the land's remaining peaceful places. She fights to protect the land and living things, bringing light and order to the mortal creatures under her care - even taking the form of a celestial beast.
Nidalee_18: A cosmic tracker and ferocious warrior, she is tasked to find newborn stars and defend them from the ever-hungry Dark Star corruptants. Darting from galaxy to galaxy in an eternal hunt, she is forever shifting her shape like the wandering stars in the sky.
Nidalee_27: Honoring Canyon's winning performance as Nidalee during the 2020 World Championship.
Nidalee_29: The Ocean Song Festival is lucky to have Nidalee as its performer stylist, with her fashion guides selling almost as much as her albums, but in reality she's here as a featured part of Yone's show. She was the first person he showed his lyrics to, and it's her honor to lend them her voice.
Nidalee_39: Adorable squeaky toy or deadly weapon? In Nidalee's claws, a Friendly Fish (TM) can be both!
